Title: Roll20 and Stronghold Kingdoms Subject to Security Breach
Description: In an article posted on TechCrunch February 14, the tech site revealed a potential 127 million compromised accounts. Following the announcement of 617 million other breached accounts, an individual compromised most of the accounts during 2018. This brings the total number of websites hit by this wave of hacker activity to 24. Though accounts had information stolen months ago, identifying data for these accounts went on sale just this week.
